          <span class="highlight-tag">斯皮亚格亚海滩</span>
          <span class="highlight-tag">圣母升天教堂</span>
          <span class="highlight-tag">Path of the Gods徒步</span>
          <span class="highlight-tag">Da Adolfo海滩俱乐部</span>
          <span class="highlight-tag">Le Sirenuse酒店</span>
        </div>
        
        <div class="tip-card">
          <h3>✨ 本地人建议</h3>
          <p><strong>最佳时间：</strong>5-6月或9-10月来访，避开7-8月的旅游高峰和高温。</p>
